### spec-site
```
Framework: Vue 3 + TypeScript + Vite
Router: vue-router 4
Styling: Vanilla CSS (no external UI library)
Pattern: SplitPaneLayout (standard layout) → new pages add Mockup + SpecPanel + Data
State: Composables (useXxxStore pattern)
DB: Turso (raw fetch + /v2/pipeline, no ORM)
Deploy: Cloudflare Pages (git push → auto-deploy)
```

### spec-site Conventions
- **New page**: Follow SplitPaneLayout pattern → Mockup + SpecPanel + Data file
- **Provide/inject**: Use string keys (not Symbol) — Vite HMR causes Symbol mismatch
- **No .js files**: All source in .ts/.vue. If .js appears alongside .ts, delete it
- **Turso**: Raw fetch + /v2/pipeline. Do not use libsql-stateless-easy (CORS issues)
{{/if}}

